Systemuser API

API to get system user information

List all system users for a system

Endpoint

GET authentication/api/v1/systemuser/vendor/bysystem/{systemId}

Scopes

Maskinporten token with scope altinn:authentication/systemregister.write

Content types

application/json

Query Parameters

systemid

The unique identifier of the registered system
